sources.title: Holy Water Joe (1971, Western) Lincoln Tate | Double-Crossed Bounty Hunter's Redemption!
sources.description:
When notorious gangster Donovan and his crew armed with a Union army cannon rob the bank holding bounty hunter Acquasanta Joe's earnings, Joe embarks on a relentless pursuit filled with twists and betrayal. As Joe navigates the treacherous world of double-crossing, he must recover his savings and outmaneuver both the rival gang members and the Union army.

Directors: Mario Gariazzo, Richard Harrison
Writers: Mario Gariazzo, Ferdinando Poggi

Main Cast:
Lincoln Tate (Acquasanta Joe / Holy Water Joe), 
Ty Hardin (Jeff/Bill Donovan), 
Richard Harrison (Charlie Bennett), 
Silvia Monelli (Estella)

Genres: Italian cinema, Action, Adventure, Drama, Western
This film is available with Italian & English audio, and subtitled in many languages.


Original title: Acquasanta Joe (1971) 
AKA: Holy Water Joe (USA) | Weihwasser Joe (Germany) | Los Violentos De Texas (Spain) | Joe eau-benite (Spain) | Acquasanta Joe (France) | Joe, o Pistoleiro (Brazil)
